      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-cnooc-makes-100-million-ton-oilfield-discovery-south-china-sea-2024-03-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国有石油天然气巨头中海油周五在一份声明中表示，该公司在南海发现了一个新的储量，探明储量超过 1 亿吨石油当量。]]></description>
